”
“ I think he ’s saving it for the deeper explanation later .  
He mostly talked about how he was going to make it his objective to make people quit , he is n’t going to pay anyone , job prospects suck , he ’s going to make people march in the heat and the cold for miles while carrying unreasonable burdens .  
The ‘ five pounds’ speech is n’t bad , you know .  
It gets through to the kids , ” Jasper said .  
For all that he was defending the speech , he smirked a bit .
“
It gets through to most , ” Cubs said .  
He was a big guy , tall , broad - shouldered , fit , with his hair cut short .  
