”
“
Us , ” Jasper said .
“
Guess
so , yeah , ” Cubs said .
I did n’t miss the glance he shot at the girl at the far end of our little sub - group .  
Cami wore an expression I might have termed ‘ resting angry face’ .   
Perpetually pissed .
All three of them , and many other members of the group besides , were dressed in similar shades as Gilpatrick .   
Blacks and grays .
