Take someone with you , if we ’re delayed , do like I discussed earlier .   
Keep an eye out .
”
Jasper saluted , turning to go .
The bus was n’t elegant , but hopefully it would take us away from vulnerable civilians or areas .
“
How is Longscratch ?
”
Tempera asked Crystalclear .
“
He ’s fine .   
Stalked off .   
He ’s keeping an eye out for trouble , ” Crystalclear said .   
He pointed up and off to one side .   
On an upper floor , it seemed , or on the roof .
“
