The ground smoked around where his boots touched pavement , and the smoke solidified into formations that looked like branches and twists of metal , all in an ashen white - grey .   
His entire body was made of the stuff , as if he wore armor made of white - grey bandages made solid and immobile by resin , all of the ends curling up and away from him in horns or branches .
I knew him , even just seeing his legs .   
