Being called a loser .
The other way was to succeed and ascend the name , to take that name and make it a title .   
The Lord of Loss had managed that .
He had been one of the villains in a big city on the West coast , and now he was one of the villains running a settlement on one of the corner worlds .   
Was it Earth - N ?   
