More news articles .   
Some capes were taking on roles as icons and iconoclasts for the various movements in the civilian sectors .   
Four hero teams led the ‘ icon’ groups .   
Advance Guard , Foresight , the Shepherds and the Attendant .
The first two were aimed at pushing forward .   
New approaches , doing things right this time .   
The opinions on what that way forward looked like it differed , feeding into the division between the two groups .
Things were changing .   
The Shepherds and Attendant had been groups divided along similar lines , but the Shepherds were self - combusting , and the remaining members were folding into the Attendant .   
There was some debate over what the name of the resulting team would be .
And then there were three , I thought .
