Really wanting something good .   
Going almost four months without , because they were n’t sure I could .   
Then having it be a chore .   
It had been better than the alternative , but a chore , to force myself to eat it right , to chew it thoroughly enough .
I swallowed hard again , not because I had another bite to swallow .
