”
Countenance asked .   
He was the second in command and the highest ranking team member in the room .   
His outfit was heavier and draped more than the others , both in how the cloth hung loose and how the armor panels were connected so they dangled from the piece above .   
The Foresight icon was in the center of his mask , like a cyclopean eye .
