I braced myself , both in balance and emotionally , then took to the air , moving slowly .   
I raised myself up to the same level as the guy at the end of the pole , staying within his field of vision so I would n’t surprise him .
They were using the powers to teleport people in .   
I could n’t see where the fade - in happened or where the teleportation destination was , but as the crowd shuffled , there were more of the people with tattoos , trashy people , and people that did n’t look like refugees .
