Sveta was perched on a rock in the midst of it all .
I looked at Kenzie ’s cube .   
One face of it was glowing .   
The projector .
That would be why they had been smiling , then .
I started my flight toward toward Tristan .
“ You ’ll regret ignoring me , ” Ashley said , behind me .
Pride , respect , they were key factors here .   
I could remember the meeting , the narrowing of the eyes .   
