” Sveta asked .
“
No .  
Hell no .  
Then I ’d feel obligated to make conversation and shit , ” Chris said .   
“
It ’s a sunny day , there ’s a breeze , the weather is perfect .  
I ’m going to sit outside and wait
and then I ’ll make my way back to the institution .
”
“ They wo n’t be bothered if you ’re late for dinner ?
” I asked .
“
So long as I ’m there by lights out , they do n’t care .  
They ’ve got twenty staff and over a thousand kids in the building with dead or missing parents .  
I eat or I feed myself ,
I mostly do the chores
I ’m assigned
