Counsel on call .   
It was common for new teams of heroes to have a lawyer available , who they could call and outline the situation to before they took action .   
Covering their asses , making sure the arrests could stick , that there was a voice with the authority and knowledge to talk to the police and courts if and when the heroes’ actions were questioned in more depth .
It was n’t a bad idea .   
It hobbled things , slowed them down , it was a bit of a headache … but having a lawyer as a hoop to jump through could restrain some of the more impulsive parts of the team .   
I ’d have to run it by them , but it made sense .
