I stepped off the roof , realized that someone was standing on the sidewalk on the far side of the street , staring at me , and saw the alarm on their faces .   
I gave them my best heroic salute as I started flying instead of falling from the roof of the two - story building .
“
Ashley and Rain are kind of quiet , ” I said , to the phone .
