We could have said more about Rain , and we had n’t .   
Rescuing him was a mission statement .
We had n’t said one word about the therapy group , or our individual issues and crises .
Much as I ’d wondered if I should mention my time in the hospital during job interviews or when applying to teams , I ’d been left the question of it here , standing before the committee .
I could be honest , say something , and they almost certainly would n’t let us do this .   
I could have mentioned my background when applying to teams , and I would have had even worse luck joining them .
Or I could stay silent .
