A few houses , a gas station that doubled as a hardware supply and grocery store , and a dentist ’s .   
Here , at least , there was a place to watch movies .   
I could imagine Rain ’s peers piling into cars and driving into the town , and the headaches that no doubt followed .
“
I ’m more interested in solutions than problems , ” I said .
She smiled slightly .   
