The woman ’s voice carried forward , but it was an inarticulate sound , one that became higher
, then a warbling shriek , followed by a gasp for air with a sound of its own .
She dropped to the ground , fingers clawing in dirt , twisting like she was trying to get away from everything at once .   
The noises she made were horrible , and I ’d heard some awful noises in my life .
Goatee guy started to approach her .   
