The woman was curled up now .   
She pulsed , and with each pulse , dark cracks ran across her body and over her clothes , then faded away .
After a few tries , she stopped trying .   
She shrieked , and then strangled the shriek .
“ Is there anything we can do for her ?
” Sveta asked .
