It did hurt , when the fingers pulled against skin closer to the bullet wound , but the massage soothed the cramp enough that the pain was worth enduring .
“ I was n’t sure if you were using super strength or if it was you , ” she said .
Then ask , I thought , the pain sharpening thoughts that might not have been so sharp five minutes ago or five minutes from now .
