” I sighed .   
I took in the scene .   
A field of weeds had been turned into mud and uprooted plants by the passage of a few hundred road ragers .   
Behind us , students were resisting the ones who were telling them that it was time to pack up , that they ’d gotten their message across and there was no reason to stay .
“
