Then I ’d turn them in anyway .
”
“ Eminently reasonable , ” I said .   
I bent down by the table , noting the various lenses and segments of metal with holes in them .   
There were computer chips that had been cannibalized , and others that had been rebuilt into Frankenstein abominations .   
“
Where do you get the money for these parts ?
”
“ Parents , ” she said .   
“
