Was that unfair ?   
Maybe it was a bad read , one way or the other , and father and daughter were more similar than that .
She ’s not your mom , and that ’s not your dad .   
I remembered Ashley ’s words .   
I ’d promised to set aside judgment , and give Kenzie ’s family a fair shake .   
There were things that were weird , but sometimes people were weird .
