We were n’t sharing information .
Time enough at last .
Either way , it tied back to my general observation : as Bakuda ’s personality had been colored by the same traits that made her ramble and rave about tech to even her captors , Armsmaster had taken the taciturn tinker approach and extrapolated it to the rest of his personality .   
He stayed by the door , silent , knuckles of one gauntlet still resting on the frame , and he volunteered no small talk .
