Being the odd one in .
Amy had been the odd one in more than I had .   
Purely average in appearance , quiet , she had n’t been passionate about hobbies or about anything in particular .   
She ’d liked movies from Aleph and when she was twelve she ’d break her usual reserved , quiet composure to get way too excited if she checked the change slot of a vending machine or pay phone and found a quarter .   
And yet when we got to high school , she was automatically included in the group of popular students .   
