I started to pull my arm into a proper headlock .   
He knew how to break it .
Had I used my strength , the Wretch would have torn him to shreds .   
This was the scenario Uncle Neil had been preparing me for when he ’d sparred with me .
I ’d sparred with Dean too .   
Roughhousing and real sparring both .   
