“
It wo n’t affect me now , ” she said .
I was n’t in a good place , and I could recognize that the inexplicable gratitude that welled up in me at hearing that was n’t good .
Focus , I thought .
We ’d been in this building before .   
It was shaped like a plus sign , with the intersection in the center being the place we ’d been held up , a heavily reinforced desk , including the gates we had to pass through .   
