“
Right ?
”
“
Would you rather be shot by them ?
”
Goddess asked , ignoring Kenzie .
“ We have to live with the consequences after , ” I said .   
“
We can do this in a good way .
”
“ One moment , ” she said .   
She paused .
I clenched my teeth , lips pressed together behind my mask .
Four hundred feet away , at one corner of a building , brick and glass shattered , a window and balcony coming to pieces .   
From what I could see of the follow - up , a series of blasts and destruction within the room she had targeted , she was removing the floor from the room .
“
That-
” I started .
“
A moment , ” she interrupted , firmer .   
