He was heavy , with the kind of double chin that hung over his collarbone .   
He had wiry stubble , and there was n’t much helping to distinguish the end of the facial hair and the start of body hair .   
His hair was short and uneven , and it was greasy , which made the uneven spikes that much more noticeable .
Most notable was his mouth .   
He looked like he had chewed on an ink packet .   
His teeth were yellow - white , but the spaces between them , the lines around his mouth and his tongue were all black .
Coalbelcher .
“ … and a villainess ?   
Heroine ?
”
“ Heroine .
