But she had eyes on the situation , and she was keeping him safe from her power , while he thrived in an environment where fire and heat were so ready at hand .
Lung ignored Byron ’s water , ignited or no , and threw out flame , walling off my access to Rain .
In the midst of it , I saw Rain using one of his lesser - used powers .   
