Fuck , I thought , and it was n’t an angry , forceful , empowered fuck , in defiance of the world .   
The fuck that I could n’t even voice was the kind of sound that came out with a whimper , that made someone sound half their age , uttered just before they broke down into tears , slumped against a wall .
