I hit the top of the vehicle I ’d been meaning to go over .   
A second had passed , I ’d stopped flying , I ’d dropped the Wretch and I ’d let go of the gun I ’d been using as a club .
Stupid , I thought .
People grabbed me .   
I twisted away and tried to roll over the trunk of the vehicle to the far side , and I found myself as weak as a baby .
Fly .   
I forced myself to fly , and it did take some forcing .   
Not because my power was weak or gone , but because my head was n’t all there .   
My thoughts were as weak as my body .
