“ Power nullification ?
”
“ Everything nullification .   
No powers , no outside help .   
You , me , and the arena .
”
I wanted to pace , to encourage him to do it too , to maintain an even distance between us .   
It did n’t happen .   
That kind of pressure and maneuvering required a roughly equivalent power .   
I had to be something more than a twenty - one year old woman , unarmed , against a man five inches taller than me who was armed with an axe .
Maybe a Trump power , but I was n’t betting anything on it .   
I knew Trump powers tended to arise , though not always , when a person triggered in relation to power - based stressors .   
I knew they tended to feel disconnected from humanity , much like breakers did , just like how movers reported being chronically restless or having trouble setting down roots .
Shaker power , yes .   
Area or environment focused .   
Changing the battlefield .   
Shaker powers fell roughly in line with contextual or environmental threats .   
They were mindful of those things , usually .   
Context .   
Environment .
“
The city ca n’t take much more of this .   
