”   
This was supposed to be a jail .
I did n’t get a decisive answer , only a muddle of ten voices talking at once .   
The dog was back on its feet now , and the Wretch was active .
I ’d fought mutant dogs before .   
Those had been a bit bigger , armor plated , with sharper edges , hooks , and decorations .   
This was … denser .   
It was the only way I could put it .   
I flew at its legs , expanding the Wretch out to knock its legs out from under it , then punted it across the floor .
